Package: RedcapLite
Type: Package
Title: A Lightweight R & REDCap Interface for Data Management
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Waiguru Muriuki <waigurusamuel@uidaho.edu>
Maintainer: Waiguru Muriuki <waigurusamuel@gmail.com>
Description: 
    RedcapLite provides a lightweight interface for interacting with 
    REDCap (Research Electronic Data Capture) via its API. 
    The package allows users to fetch raw data or preprocess it by 
    adding value labels, handling checkbox fields, and assigning 
    column attributes. Designed for flexibility and efficiency, 
    RedcapLite supports data retrieval for both longitudinal and 
    non-longitudinal projects. The package also facilitates saving 
    processed data in reusable formats.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
